		<title>Back to the Future with Cross-Context Dispatch</title>
		<link>https://webtide.com/back-to-the-future-with-cross-context-dispatch/</link>
					<comments>https://webtide.com/back-to-the-future-with-cross-context-dispatch/#respond</comments>
		
